Capital Markets

Company Overview of Trillium Asset Management LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Trillium Asset Management LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals and high net worth individuals. It also caters to Trusts, corporate pension and profit sharing plans, Taft Hartley plans, charitable institutions, for profit and non profit institutional clients, foundations, endowments, municipalities, registered mutual funds, private investment funds and trust programs. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. It also manages balanced mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. It invests in income and growth stocks...
Trillium Asset Management LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals and high net worth individuals. It also caters to Trusts, corporate pension and profit sharing plans, Taft Hartley plans, charitable institutions, for profit and non profit institutional clients, foundations, endowments, municipalities, registered mutual funds, private investment funds and trust programs. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. It also manages balanced mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. It invests in income and growth stocks of companies across all capitalizations. The firm employs GARP and core investing style to make its equity investments. It employs a top-down approach to select its sectors and a fundamental, quantitative analysis, and technical analysis to create its equity portfolio mix. The firm benchmarks the performance of its equity portfolios against the S&P 500, S&P 1000, and S&P 1500 indices. For the fixed income portfolios, it invests in investment grade intermediate-term corporate, government agency, and municipal bonds. The firm makes socially and environmentally responsible community-based investments. It conducts in-house research to make its investments. Trillium Asset Management was founded in 1982 and is based in Boston, Massachusetts with additional offices in San Francisco, California, Portland, Oregon, and Durham, North Carolina.
Detailed Description


