Lisa MacKinnon






Trillium Asset Management  »  » Lisa MacKinnon












 
Lisa MacKinnonInvestment Manager


Lisa MacKinnon is an Investment Manager and serves as a steward and builder of relationships with clients, prospects and partners – with a focus on individual and institutional investors.
Prior to joining Trillium in 1993, Lisa worked as a marketer for an environmental technology company. She is active in her community and is a past co-President of the local Junior Women’s Club. Lisa previously served on Trillium’s board of directors.
Lisa earned her B.S. in Management (Concentration in Marketing) from the University of Massachusetts Boston College of Management.
